{"tid":1717212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歷史堂] 阻止車輛/坦克前進最佳路障: 捷克刺蝟 Czech Hedgehog","createTime":"2019-11-13T14:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T04:25:40.000Z","uid":26332,"like":128,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"9f605dd7cb774e9ae1bc8f5297814c1b472c9142","tid":1717212,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捷克刺蝟<br />\nCzech Hedgehog</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n捷克刺蝟（捷克語：rozsoch&aacute;č）又稱反坦克拒馬，是一種固定的反坦克障礙物，由金屬隅梁或工字梁構成。捷克刺蝟組成的防線能有效阻止坦克進攻。甚至在當其附近發生爆炸後，仍能繼續發揮作用。儘管它能為攻方步兵提供部分有限的防禦，但步兵在對抗守衛森嚴的防禦陣地時，戰力通常遠低於被捷克刺蝟阻礙的機械化步兵部隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/19/Bundesarchiv_Bild_101I-719-0240-26%2C_Pas_de_Calais%2C_Atlantikwall%2C_Panzersperren.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F19%2FBundesarchiv_Bild_101I-719-0240-26%252C_Pas_de_Calais%252C_Atlantikwall%252C_Panzersperren.jpg&h=fca61b5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E1gGsNj6s8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE1gGsNj6s8U&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey9OI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=81512736\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E1gGsNj6s8U</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28bdb5bc7253137d35365fc6810595115ff092f","tid":1717212,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c98445d6e8674a4625722b23193e5765789cbac","tid":1717212,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T14:19:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d063bf52309ba26993634ad1edc4c5d7ba42a435","tid":1717212,"uid":26332,"li